name: Beer : An experimental evolution
description: Taking something and turning into something else. Transmutation. What is more valuable, the result, or the cause? This picture is the root Metadata to OBJKT#53706, OBJKT#53785, OBJKT#53838, OBJKT#53875, OBJKT#53915, OBJKT#54079 and OBJKT#55610. Without this image, none of those objkt would exist. Without the artist, you would not have the art, without the muse, the artist would not have the inspiration to create. So what is worth more? The art, or the muse?
